*** De chay duoc demo can thuc hien cac buoc sau:

0. Build cac tool cua HTK-3.4.1 (vi du, HCopy, HVite,..) va copy tat ca binary files vao thu muc ./HTK_spkDepDemo/HTK-3.4.1/bin
1. Chuyen den lam viec tai thư mục HTK_spkDepDemo.
2. Go "./runDemo" de chay demo. Perl script nay la phien ban rut gon cua script goc ./runDemo.pl.
3. Khi Perl script nay chay xong, xem:
- Ket qua nhan dang tren toan bo du lieu huan luyen (goi la Closed test) trong file ./result/trainResult.
(ket qua nhan dang cua tung file trong thu muc ./result/train).
- Ket qua nhan dang tren toan bo du lieu kiem thu (goi la Open test) trong file ./result/testResult.
(ket qua nhan dang cua tung file trong thu muc ./result/test).

*** De thu nghiem cac cau hinh HMM khac nhau, chinh sua noi dung cua 2 files & xem ket qua thay doi ntn:
./configs/monPlainM1S1.dcf va ./protoconfigs/proto.pcf

